nd 'እና'.\n\nSix strings were discarded due to being unfixable OCR errors, gibberish, or incomplete words: 'ጥቃዋስ', 'ጥቃዘር' (a duplicate of a previously discarded item), 'ጥቅማጥ', 'ጥቅር', 'ጥቅ፟ን', and 'ጥበልያ'. 'ጥቅ፟ን' was specifically discarded due to the unusual and misplaced gemination mark '፟' making it semantically unrecoverable.\n\nFor the remaining valid words, roots were extracted, parts of speech assigned, and comprehensive English synonyms provided. Scholarly guesses were made for the root of 'በተለያዩ' (from 'መለያየት') and 'ከሌሎች' (from 'ሌላ'), and 'በቅርቡ' (from 'ቅርብ'), reflecting their morphological origins and functional roles.","input_words":["ጥቃቷ","ጥቃዋስ","ጥቃዘር","ጥቅሉም","ጥቅሎቹ","ጥቅሎችንና","ጥቅማጥ","ጥቅማጥቀሞችን","ጥቅማጥቅሙ","ጥቅማጥቅሞቹ","ጥቅማጥቅሞቼ","ጥቅምምንም","ጥቅምከሌሎች","ጥቅሞቹበቅርቡ","ጥቅር","ጥቅሶችእንደ","ጥቅ፟ን","ጥቅዘር","ጥቍረት","ጥበልያ","ጥበቃዎቻቸውንና","ጥበቆቹ","ጥበቆች","ጥበበኞቹም","ጥበበኞቹና","ጥበበኞችሽ","ጥበበኞችዋ","ጥበበኞችዋንም","ጥበባትበተለያዩ","ጥበብቀደምትና"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"3f6bafcc-1a25-4de0-8f21-1be65b7cd526","created_at":"2026-03-02T22:14:36.034249+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_25/chunk_0663.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጥንት","word":"ጥንተ","synonyms":["ancient","origin","antiquity","primeval"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መታጠር","word":"ታጠር","synonyms":["to be fenced","to be enclosed","to be surrounded"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጥንት","word":"ጥንታችሁ","synonyms":["ancient","origin","antiquity","primeval"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ጥንት","word":"ጥንታዉያን","synonyms":["ancient","primeval","old","archaic"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጥንካሬ","word":"ጥንካሬህ","synonyms":["strength","firmness","toughness","resilience","vigor"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Adjective","root":"ጥንክር","word":"ጥንክር","synonyms":["strong","firm","tough","sturdy","robust"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አመድ","word":"አመድ","synonyms":["ash","cinder","embers"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጥንክር","word":"ጥንክርነት","