],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ሚዲያ","word":"ሚዲያ","synonyms":["media"],"importance":7}],"summary":"The input batch contained 30 strings. Through the 8 scholarly protocols, 29 valid Amharic words were extracted, corrected, lemmatized, and tagged. \n\n**Protocol 1: The Splitter (De-cluttering)**\n- Merged words were successfully split: 'ጥንተታጠር' into 'ጥንተ' and 'ታጠር'; 'ጥንታችሁም' into 'ጥንታችሁ' and 'ም'; 'ጥንካሬህና' into 'ጥንካሬህ' and 'ና'; 'ጥንክራመድ' into 'ጥንክር' and 'አመድ'; 'ጥንዶችስለዚህ' into 'ጥንዶች' and 'ስለዚህ'; 'ጥዋዎችም' into 'ጥዋዎች' and 'ም'; 'ጥያቄሩቅ' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'ሩቅ'; 'ጥያቄበሙዚየሙ' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'በሙዚየሙ'; 'ጥያቄበኦሮሞና' into 'ጥያቄ', 'በኦሮሞ', and 'ና'; 'ጥያቄበገዳም' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'በገዳም'; 'ጥያቄበጉዱማሌ' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'በጉዱማሌ'; 'ጥያቄአቶ' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'አቶ'; 'ጥያቄከሁለት' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'ከሁለት'; 'ጥያቄከሃብት' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'ከሃብት'; 'ጥያቄከሦስት' into 'ጥያቄ' and 'ከሦስት'; 'ጥያቄዎችሚዲያ' into 'ጥያቄዎች' and 'ሚዲያ'.\n\n**Protocol 2: The Judge (Nonsense Removal)**\n- Five strings were discarded as unfixable OCR errors or gibberish: 'ጥንዎት', 'ጥንድርስ', 'ጥንድርጉ', 'ጥንፋደግ', and 'ጥዘዜት'. These strings did not correspond to any recognizable Amharic words or could not be reliably corrected.\n\n**Protocol 3: The Corrector (Visual Repair)**\n- Several OCR errors were corrected based on common confusions and linguistic context: 'ጥኣቄዎቹን' was corrected to 'ጥያቄዎቹን'; 'ጥኣቄዎች' to 'ጥያቄዎች'; 'ጥየቄን' to 'ጥያቄን'; and 'ጥያቁ' to 'ጥያቄ'. No punctuation stripping was required.\n\n**Protocol 4: The Lemmatizer (Global Citation Form)**\n- Base dictionary forms (roots) were identified for all valid words, including complex morphological structures. For example, 'ጥንተ' was lemmatized to 'ጥንት', 'ታጠር' to 'መታጠር', 'ጥንካሬህ' to 'ጥንካሬ', 'ጥንዶች' to 'ጥንድ', and 'ጥያቄዎቹን' to 'ጥያቄ'.\n\n**Protocol 7: The Filter (Size Constraint)**\n- The single-character particle 'ም' (from 'ጥንታችሁም' and 'ጥዋዎችም') was discarded as per the rule requiring words to be at least 2 characters long.\n\n**Scholarly Guesses:**\n- 'ጥንተ' was interpreted as a form derived from 'ጥንት' (ancient/origin) due to its com